1.name: Total of line item quantities
1.desc: Algebraic total of the quantity values in line items in a message.

2.name: Number of line items in message
2.desc: Total number of line items in the message.

3.name: Number of line and sub items in message
3.desc: Total number of line and sub items in the message.

4.name: Number of invoice lines
4.desc: Number of lines on an invoice.

5.name: Number of Customs item detail lines
5.desc:
Total number of occurrences of the Customs item detail section within
                                    a single Customs declaration message.

6.name: Number of Customs entries
6.desc:
Number of entries which are subject to the same Customs procedures,
                                    and have the same tariff or statistical heading, country and duty regime.

7.name: Total gross weight
7.desc: Code to indicate total gross weight of a consignment.

9.name: Total number of ULD (Unit Load Device)
9.desc: The total number of Unit Load Devices mentioned in the message.

11.name: Total number of packages
11.desc: [7370] Total number of packages of the entire consignment.

12.name: Invoice total amount
12.desc:
[5444] Total sum charged in respect of one or more Invoices in
                                    accordance with the terms of delivery.

13.name: Number of loading lists
13.desc:
[1166] Number of loading lists, manifests or other similar
                                    specifications attached to a document.

14.name: Number of Customs commercial detail lines
14.desc: Commercial detail section within a single Customs declaration message.

16.name: Total number of equipment
16.desc: Total number of equipment mentioned in the message.

17.name: Declared total Customs value
17.desc:
[5070] Total value declared for Customs purposes of all goods in a
                                    consignment, whether or not they are subject to the same Customs procedure, or have
                                    the same tariff/statistical heading, country information, and duty regime.

18.name: Total reported quantity in net weight
18.desc: Total reported quantity in net weight.

19.name: Total reported quantity in supplementary units
19.desc: Total reported quantity in supplementary units.

20.name: Total reported invoice(s) value
20.desc: Hash total of the total monetary amounts reported on the invoices.

21.name: Total reported ancillary costs
21.desc:
Hash total of the reported total extra costs (e.g. carriage, freight,
                                    insurance) of all invoices.

23.name: Total ordered quantity
23.desc: Total quantity ordered in this message.

24.name: Number of orders referenced in this message
24.desc:
Total number of order messages or documents referenced in this
                                    message.

25.name: Number of rejected order lines
25.desc: Total number of rejected order lines in this message.

26.name: Total gross measurement/cube
26.desc:
Total gross cubic measurement of the goods, including packing but
                                    excluding transport equipment.

27.name: Total number of credit items given for control purposes
27.desc: Total number of credit items given for control purposes.

28.name: Total number of debit items given for control purposes
28.desc: Total number of debit items given for control purposes.

29.name: Total net weight of consignment
29.desc: A code to indicate the total net weight of a consignment.

30.name: Total number of empty containers
30.desc: The total number of empty containers mentioned in the message.

31.name: Number of messages
31.desc: Control count of the number of messages referenced.

32.name: Total gross weight of the goods within the means of transport
32.desc:
Weight (mass) of the goods within the means of transport, including
                                    packing and excluding the carrier's equipment.

33.name: Total number of original Bills of Lading
33.desc:
Total number of the original Bills of Lading required for the
                                    consignment.

34.name: Total number of copy Bills of Lading
34.desc: Total number of copy Bills of Lading required for the consignment.

35.name: Number of containers to be discharged
35.desc: Number of containers to be discharged from the means of transport.

36.name: Number of containers to be loaded
36.desc: Number of containers to be loaded in or on the means of transport.

37.name: Number of containers to be restowed
37.desc: Number of containers to be restowed from one cell position to another.

38.name: Number of containers to be shifted
38.desc: Number of containers to be shifted from one cell position to another.

39.name: Total number of individual transactions
39.desc: The total number of individual transactions.

40.name: Total number of sequence details in message
40.desc: The total number of sequence details in the message.

42.name: Total number of passengers
42.desc: The total number of passengers aboard the conveyance.

43.name: Total number of work tasks
43.desc: Total number of work tasks in the message.

44.name: Total number of milestones
44.desc: Total number of milestones in the message.

45.name: Total number of available resources
45.desc: Total number of available resources in the message.

46.name: Total number of constraints
46.desc: Total number of constraints in the message.

47.name: Total wholesaler unsold quantity
47.desc: Total quantity of unsold goods held by the wholesaler.

48.name: Total quantity held by delivery vehicles
48.desc: Total quantity held by the delivery vehicles.

49.name: Total quantity held by retail outlets
49.desc: Total quantity held by the retail outlets.

50.name: Total rejected return quantity
50.desc: The total quantity for return which have been rejected.

51.name: Number of goods items in the message
51.desc: The total number of goods items in a message.

52.name: Number of patients
52.desc: The number of patients reported in a message.

53.name: Hash total of reported debit items
53.desc:
Hash total of the values of all the debit item amounts reported in the
                                    message.

54.name: Hash total of reported credit items
54.desc:
Hash total of the values of all the credit item amounts reported in
                                    the message.

56.name: Total number of transport units
56.desc:
Number of separate units of cargo handled during transportation of a
                                    consignment.

57.name: Total loading metres
57.desc: The total number of loading metres.
